45:12.666 --> 45:15.756
If I start thrashing around
or pulling my clothes off,

45:15.930 --> 45:18.367
you all gotta
promise to stop me.

45:19.151 --> 45:21.153
It he's naked and
starts thrashing around,

45:21.327 --> 45:23.721
I'm gonna have to
